 A Lagos-based estate firm, Silver Pacific Homes, has launched two estates – Kingsmark Estate and Royal County 3 – at Abijo, Ibeju-Lekki, close to the Free Trade Zone in Ibeju-Lekki. Managing Director Samuel Ikoje said “Kingsmark Estate has a Cof O as title and it’s a buy and build estate… Both are proximal to the lagoon front… suitable for both commercial and residential purposes.” Ikoje stressed that Silver Pacific Homes was poised to simplify property acquisition and deliver same at affordable prices in choice locations. He said the estate’s features include dry land, electricity, gated house, road network, perimeter fenceand recreation centre. Ikoje assured buyers that instant allocation was guaranteed after payment.